find out more about some of

00:41:21.810 --> 00:41:26.280
these topics, like affordances
and natural mapping, an in Don

00:41:26.280 --> 00:41:30.030
Norman's book, or the mental
models in Alan Cooper's

00:41:30.030 --> 00:41:31.920
classic, About Face.

00:41:31.920 --> 00:41:35.940
And for typography and layout,
one of my favorites is The

00:41:35.940 --> 00:41:37.790
