00:52:07.220 --> 00:52:09.080
standardized for that.

00:52:09.080 --> 00:52:11.300
And it helps users so much.

00:52:11.300 --> 00:52:13.150
ALEX FAABORG: Yeah and
especially thinking about your

00:52:13.150 --> 00:52:15.530
users, because you're going to
